    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那从入口到未初始化是直接连接吗？还有，未初始化状态下可以触发哪些操作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[Retail_CustomerLoyalty]",
