    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，入口直接指向未初始化。在未初始化状态下，可以执行InitializeCA进入初始化中，也可以直接执行UpdateConfiguration进入重新配置状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Uninitialized",
        "Initializing",
        "InitializeCA",
